## Misc
*.log
# launchSettings.json is intentionally TRACKED for pr-inbox so that
# `dotnet run` on a fresh clone lands on the right port + Development
# environment. Otherwise the app defaults to port 5000 / Production,
# which silently breaks Blazor's _framework/blazor.web.js serving.
